    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents a superlative example of naturally aspirated engineering, powered by the S65 4.0L V8 featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a lightning-fast M-DCT dual-clutch transmission and a variable M differential lock for surgical power delivery. Mechanically, the vehicle is flawless: rod bearings have been addressed as preventative maintenance, the rear subframe is pristine, and the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) provides factory-spec damping across all modes. With zero fluid seepage and a heat-cycle history indicative of careful ownership, this is a turn-key apex predator for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48900.0,
